name: 'APEG'
description:
Much like the cryptopunk derivative fomo storm of early 2021 the bored monkey boat club has errupted into a behemoth brand. Even though only created this year they have quickly risen to the top of the NFT food chain. With their IRL events and literal yacht club this PFP project has grown into an elitist celebrity cult, with more variations and collabs adding to the rule 34 of this fast growing brand. 

But hey all of this is above my paygrade anyway, what do I know.. guess I shoulda aped in when I had the chance :)
